    <div class="info">
      <p> The Italian Greyhound is a small dog that weighs roughly 7-14 pounds and lives for an average of 14-15 years. They have a short coat length and are described as alert, playful and sensitive. </p>

      <p> <a href="https://www.akc.org/dog-breeds/italian-greyhound/"> See more information about the Italian Greyhound from the American Kennel Club. </a> </p>

